paper/index.qmd-2-title: "MacKenzie Scott's giving, in QALYs"
paper/index.qmd:3:subtitle: "An evidence-weighted, auditable cost-effectiveness model of a $26 billion portfolio"
paper/index.qmd-4-bibliography: references.bib
