./docs/review/round1/red-team.out.ipynb:70:    "    **Concrete fix:** Re-render the canonical manuscript before circulation. Interpolate every model-derived number, create tests for externally typed constants and their denominators, and fail CI when the rendered text/PDF is older than or semantically inconsistent with `index.qmd` and the result artifacts.\n",
